==============================
|ID|OPERATOR            |NAME|
------------------------------
|0 |SUBPLAN SCAN        |rw  |
|1 | RECURSIVE UNION ALL|    |
|2 |  TABLE SCAN        |emp1|
|3 |  HASH JOIN         |    |
|4 |   TABLE SCAN       |t   |
|5 |   TABLE SCAN       |r   |
==============================

